Label: 标签
Open for Clip Aesthetic!: 打开以调整美术风格（Clip Aesthetic）！
Aesthetic imgs embedding: 美术风格图集嵌入（Images Embedding）
Enable scribble mode if your image has w: 如果图像背景是白色，请启用涂鸦模式。
Prompts from file or textbox: 从文本框或文件载入提示词
Put variable parts at start of prompt: 把可变部分放在提示词开头
Use different seed for each picture: 为每张图用不同随机种子
Select joining char: 提示词之间用什么连接符
Iterate seed every line: 每行输入更换随机种子
Use same random seed for all lines: 每行输入用同一随机种子
Artist or styles name list. '.txt' files: 艺术家或风格列表，每行一个，以'.txt'结尾
Prompt Placeholder, which can be used at: 提示词位符，可在提示输入的顶部使用
Process images in a directory on the sam: 处理服务器中某目录的图片，
Use an empty output directory to save pi: 输出到单独的空目录（而非默认输出目录）
Add inpaint batch mask directory to enab: Add inpaint batch mask directory to enable inpaint batch processing.
Inpaint batch mask directory (required f: Inpaint batch mask directory (required for inpaint batch processing only)
Crop and resize: 裁剪并缩放（保持宽高比）
Resize and fill: 缩放并填充（保持宽高比）
Image CFG Scale: 图片提示词相关性（Image CFG Scale）
img2img alternative test: 图生图替代测试（img2img alternative test）
Poor man's outpainting: 穷把式的外部扩绘（Poor man's outpainting）
Override `Sampling method` to Euler?(thi: 覆写 `采样方法` 为 Euler？（此方法是为它设计的）
Override `prompt` to the same value as `: 以 `原提示词` 覆写 `提示词`？（`反向提示词` 同理）
Override `Sampling Steps` to the same va: 以 `解码步数` 覆写 `采样步数`？
Decode CFG scale: 解码提示词相关性（Decode CFG scale）
Sigma adjustment for finding noise for i: 用于发现图片噪声的 Sigma 调整（adjustment）
Recommended settings: Sampling Steps: 80: 推荐设置： 采样步数：80-100； 采样方法：Euler a； 去噪强度：0.8
Fall-off exponent (lower=higher detail): 衰减指数（Fall-off exponent）（越小细节越好）
Will upscale the image by the selected s: 会按放大系数放大图片；用宽度和高度滑块设置图块尺寸
CodeFormer weight (0 = maximum effect, 1: CodeFormer 权重（为 0 时影响最大；为 1 时影响最小）
A weighted sum will be used for interpol: A weighted sum will be used for interpolation. Requires two models; A and B. The result is calculated as A * (1 - M) + B * M
Multiplier (M) - set to 0 to get model A: 模型比例（M）- 为 0 则等同于模型 A
Name: 名称
Number of vectors per token: 每个 token 的向量个数
Select activation function of hypernetwo: 选择超网络激活函数（activation function）；推荐：Swish 或 Linear（无）
Select Layer weights initialization. Rec: 选择网络层权重初始化方式；按激活函数推荐：类 relu - Kaiming；类 sigmoid - Xavier；其他 - Normal
Enter hypernetwork Dropout structure (or: Enter hypernetwork Dropout structure (or empty). Recommended : 0~0.35 incrementing sequence: 0, 0.05, 0.15
Existing Caption txt Action: 对既存描述文本 txt 的行为
Use BLIP for caption: 用 BLIP 生成说明文本
Use deepbooru for caption: 用 deepbooru 生成说明文本
Each image is center-cropped with an aut: 每张图片以自动选择的宽度和高度居中裁切。
Train an embedding or Hypernetwork; you: 训练一个模型嵌入或超网络；必须指定一个具有 1:1 比例图片集的目录
Save an image to log directory every N s: 每 N 步保存一张图片到日志目录，0 为禁用
Save a copy of embedding to log director: 每 N 步保存模型嵌入的副本到日志目录，0 为禁用
Save images with embedding in PNG chunks: 保存图片时将模型嵌入存入 PNG 数据块
Read parameters (prompt, etc...) from tx: 预览时从文生图（txt2img）选项卡读取参数（提示词等）
Shuffle tags by ',' when creating prompt: 创建提示词时按 “,” 区分并打乱标签
创建提示词时随机舍弃标签
Create an aesthetic embedding out of any: 从任意张图片创建美术风格嵌入（Aesthetic Embedding）
To activate inspiration function, you ne: To activate inspiration function, you need get "inspiration" images first.
You can create these images by run \"Cre: You can create these images by run "Create inspiration images" script in txt2img page,
you can get the artists or art styles li: you can get the artists or art styles list from here
download these files, and select these f: download these files, and select these files in the "Create inspiration images" script UI
There about 6000 artists and art styles: There about 6000 artists and art styles in these files.
This takes server hours depending on you: This takes server hours depending on your GPU type and how many pictures  you generate for each artist/style
I suggest at least four images for each: I suggest at least four images for each
You can also download generated pictures: You can also download generated pictures from here:
and restart webui, and enjoy the joy of: and restart webui, and enjoy the joy of creation!
Always save all generated images: 始终保存所有生成的图片
Add number to filename when saving: 保存时在文件名中加入数字
Always save all generated image grids: 始终保存所有生成的宫格图
Add extended info (seed, prompt) to file: 在宫格图文件名中加入额外信息（随机种子、提示词）
Do not save grids consisting of one pict: 不保存只有单张图片的宫格图
Prevent empty spots in grid (when set to: （在自动检测时）防止宫格图中出现空位
Grid row count; use -1 for autodetect an: 宫格图行数；-1 为自动检测；0 为与批量（Batch size）相同
Save text information about generation p: 生成参数相关的文本信息作为数据块存入 PNG 文件中
Create a text file next to every image w: 保存图片时在其旁边创建文本文件记录生成参数
Save a copy of image before doing face r: 面部修复前保存图片副本
Save a copy of image before applying hig: 高分辨率修复前保存图片副本
Save a copy of image before applying col: 对图生图结果做颜色校正前保存图片副本
If PNG image is larger than 4MB or any d: 当 PNG 图片大于 4MB 或某一维大于 4000 像素时，缩小并保存副本为 JPG
Use original name for output filename du: 附加（Extras）选项卡中，批处理时用原始名称作为输出文件名
Use upscaler name as filename suffix in: 在附加选项卡中把放大算法名称用作文件名后缀
When using 'Save' button, only save a si: 用 “保存” 按钮时，只保存单张选中的图片
Directory for temporary images; leave em: 临时图片目录；默认留空
Cleanup non-default temporary directory: 启动时清理非默认临时目录
Output directory for images; if empty, d: 图片输出目录；若为空，则默认为以下三个目录
Output directory for grids; if empty, de: 宫格图输出目录；若为空，则默认为以下两个目录
Output directory for txt2img grids: 文生图（txt2img）宫格图输出目录
Output directory for img2img grids: 图生图（img2img）宫格图输出目录
Directory for saving images using the Sa: 用 “保存” 按钮将图片保存到的目录
When using \"Save\" button, save images: 用 “保存” 按钮时，保存图片到子目录
Max prompt words for [prompt_words] patt: [prompt_words] 模板中提示词词的最大个数
Tile size for ESRGAN upscalers. 0 = no t: ESRGAN 系放大算法的图块尺寸；0 为不分块
Tile overlap, in pixels for ESRGAN upsca: ESRGAN 系放大算法的图块重叠像素数；较小时缝隙明显
LDSR processing steps. Lower = faster: LDSR 处理步数；越少越快
Cache LDSR model in memory: 缓存 LDSR 模型至内存
SwinIR 系放大算法的图块尺寸
Tile overlap, in pixels for SwinIR. Low: SwinIR 系放大算法的图块重叠像素数；较小时缝隙明显
CodeFormer weight parameter; 0 = maximum: CodeFormer 权重参数；为 0 时影响最大；为 1 时影响最小
Move face restoration model from VRAM in: 完成处理后将面部修复模型从显存移至内存
VRAM usage polls per second during gener: 生成时每秒轮询显存用量次数；0 为禁用
Always print all generation info to stan: 始终打印所有生成信息至标准输出（standard output）
Add a second progress bar to the console: 为控制台增加第二进度条，显示整体作业进度
Print extra hypernetwork information to: Print extra hypernetwork information to console.
Move VAE and CLIP to RAM when training i: 训练时试着移动 VAE 和 CLIP 模型至内存，节省显存
Turn on pin_memory for DataLoader. Makes: 为数据加载器（DataLoader）启用 pin_memory；略微加快训练但也增加内存占用
Saves Optimizer state as separate *.opti: Saves Optimizer state as separate *.optim file. Training of embedding or HN can be resumed with the matching optim file.
Save textual inversion and hypernet sett: 每当训练开始时，将textual inversion和hypernet设置保存到文本文件中。
Filename word regex: 文件名词语提取正则表达式
Number of repeats for a single input ima: 每轮（epoch）重复单张输入图片的次数； 只用于显示轮数
Save an csv containing the loss to log d: 每 N 步保存一个包含损失值（loss）的 csv 文件到日志目录，0 为禁用
Use cross attention optimizations while: 训练时启用交叉注意力（cross attention）优化
How often, in seconds, to flush the pend: 每隔多久将tensorboard事件和摘要写入磁盘（以秒为单位）
Checkpoints to cache in RAM: 缓存至内存中的模型数
Ignore selected VAE for stable diffusion: 为旁边有同名 .vae.pt 的模型（Checkpoint）忽略选中的 VAE
Inpainting conditioning mask strength: 局部重绘（Inpaint）调节遮罩强度
Apply color correction to img2img result: 对图生图（img2img）结果应用颜色校正以匹配原图颜色
With img2img, do exactly the amount of s: 图生图时，确切做完指定的采样步数（通常降噪强度较小时要做的步数也较少）
With img2img, fill image's transparent p: 图生图时，用此颜色填充图片的透明部分
Enable quantization in K samplers for sh: 为 K 采样方法启用量化以获得更清晰、干净的结果；这可能会改变现有的随机种子；应用设置后需重启
Emphasis: use (text) to make model pay m: 强调记号：提示词中用 (文本) 吸引模型关注，用 [文本] 减少模型关注
Make K-diffusion samplers produce same i: 让 K-diffusion 采样方法在批量生成与单张生成时图片产出一致
Increase coherency by padding from the l: 所用 token 超过 75 个时，从 n 个 token 中的最后一个逗号开始填充，以提高一致性
Upcast cross attention layer to float32: Upcast cross attention layer to float32
Use old emphasis implementation. Can be: 用旧的强调记号实现，可用于复现旧随机种子
Use old karras scheduler sigmas (0.1 to: Use old karras scheduler sigmas (0.1 to 10).
For hires fix, use width/height sliders: 高分辨率修复时，用宽度/高度滑块设置最终分辨率，而非首次 (同时禁用重设宽/高度功能)
Interrogate: keep models in VRAM: 反推提示词：在显存中保留模型
Interrogate: include ranks of model tags: 反推提示词：在结果中包括模型标签（model tags）匹配的等级（对基于说明文本的反推没有影响）
Interrogate: num_beams for BLIP: 反推提示词：BLIP 的 beams 数（num_beams）
Interrogate: minimum description length: 反推提示词：最小描述长度（不包括画师等）
Interrogate: maximum description length: 反推提示词：最大描述长度
CLIP: maximum number of lines in text fi: CLIP：文本文件中的最大行数（0 为无限制）
Interrogate: deepbooru score threshold: 反推提示词：deepbooru 分数阈值
Interrogate: deepbooru sort alphabetical: 反推提示词：deepbooru 结果按字母顺序排序
use spaces for tags in deepbooru: 在 deepbooru 标签中用空格
escape (\\) brackets in deepbooru (so th: 为 deepbooru 转义 (\) 括号（使其作为括号字符而非强调记号）
filter out those tags from deepbooru out: 从 deepbooru 输出中过滤这些标签（以英文逗号隔开）
Add hypernetwork to prompt: 将超网络（hypernetwork）添加到提示词
Apply Lora to outputs rather than inputs: 如果可以，将Lora应用于输出而不是输入（实验性）
Show grid in results for web: 在网页结果栏中显示宫格图
Do not show any images in results for we: 不在网页结果栏中显示任何图片
Add model hash to generation information: 添加模型哈希值（hash）到生成信息
Add model name to generation information: 添加模型名称到生成信息
When reading generation parameters from: 从文本（PNG 信息或粘贴的文本）读入生成参数到用户界面时，不更改选定的模型
Send seed when sending prompt or image t: 传提示词或图片到其他界面时也传随机种子
Send size when sending prompt or image t: 传提示词或图片到其他界面时也传图片尺寸
Show images zoomed in by default in full: 在全页图片查看器中默认显示放大的图片
Show generation progress in window title: 在窗口标题显示生成进度
Use dropdown for sampler selection inste: Use dropdown for sampler selection instead of radio group
Show Width/Height and Batch sliders in s: Show Width/Height and Batch sliders in same row
Localization (requires restart): 本地化（应用设置后需重启）
Show live previews of the created image: Show live previews of the created image
Show previews of all images generated in: 以宫格图形式预览一批中生成的所有图片
Show new live preview image every N samp: Show new live preview image every N sampling steps. Set to -1 to show after completion of batch.
Image creation progress preview mode: 图片生成进度预览模式
Hide samplers in user interface (require: 在用户界面中隐藏以下采样方法（应用设置后需重启）
eta (noise multiplier) for ancestral sam: ancestral 系采样方法 eta（噪声因数）
img2img DDIM discretize: 图生图 DDIM 离散化
Eta noise seed delta: Eta 噪声下随机种子偏移量（delta）
Enable postprocessing operations in txt2: Enable postprocessing operations in txt2img and img2img tabs
Maximum number of images in upscaling ca: Maximum number of images in upscaling cache
Record accessable images directories: 记录可访问的图片目录
Print image deletion messages to the con: 向控制台打印图片删除信息
Maximum number of samples, used to deter: Maximum number of samples, used to determine which folders to skip when continue running the create script
Config file for Control Net models: Config file for Control Net models
Extra path to scan for ControlNet models: Extra path to scan for ControlNet models (e.g. training output directory)
Apply transfer control when loading mode: Apply transfer control when loading models
Do not append detectmap to output: Do not append detectmap to output
Use mid-layer control on highres pass (s: Use mid-layer control on highres pass (second pass)
Allow other script to control this exten: Allow other script to control this extension
Active in txt2img (Requires restart): 在文生图中启用（应用设置后需重启）
Active in img2img (Requires restart): 在图生图中启用（应用设置后需重启）
Active in negative prompts (Requires res: 在反向提示词中启用（应用设置后需重启）
Active in third party textboxes [Dataset: 在 [Dataset Tag Editor] 扩展的文本框中启用（应用设置后需重启）
List of model names (with file extension: List of model names (with file extension) or their hashes to use as black/whitelist, separated by commas.
Mode to use for model list: Mode to use for model list
Time in ms to wait before triggering com: 再次触发补全的毫秒数（应用设置后需重启）
Show '?' next to tags, linking to its Da: Show '?' next to tags, linking to its Danbooru or e621 wiki page (Warning: This is an external site and very likely contains NSFW examples!)
Replace underscores with spaces on inser: 插入时替换下划线为空格
Append comma on tag autocompletion: 自动补全标签后附加逗号
Translation file uses old 3-column trans: 翻译文件用旧的三列格式（而非新的两列格式）
Extra filename (for small sets of custom: Extra filename (for small sets of custom tags)
Mode to add the extra tags to the main t: Mode to add the extra tags to the main tag list
Reload custom script bodies (No ui updat: 重载自定义脚本（无界面更新、不重启）
Parts of CodeFormer code had to be copie: Parts of CodeFormer code had to be copied to be compatible with GFPGAN.

Hide extensions with tags: 隐藏有以下标签的扩展
URL for extension's git repository: 扩展的 git 仓库链接
Prompt (press Ctrl+Enter or Alt+Enter to: 提示词（按 Ctrl+Enter 或 Alt+Enter 生成图片）
Negative prompt (press Ctrl+Enter or Alt: 反向提示词 （按 Ctrl+Enter 或 Alt+Enter 生成图片）
Stop processing images and return any re: 停止处理，返回既存结果
Stop processing current image and contin: 跳过当前图片，继续处理
Read generation parameters from prompt o: 从提示词读取生成参数，若无提示词，则从上次生成中读取，并填补至界面
Apply selected styles to current prompt: 在提示词中应用选中样式
Euler Ancestral - very creative, each ca: Euler Ancestral - very creative, each can get a completely different picture depending on step count, setting steps higher than 30-40 does not help
How many times to improve the generated: How many times to improve the generated image iteratively; higher values take longer; very low values can produce bad results
Classifier Free Guidance Scale - how str: Classifier Free Guidance Scale - 图应与提示词一致的程度——数值越小越能产生有创意的结果
A value that determines the output of ra: 用于决定随机数生成器输出的值——参数和随机种子完全相同时产生的图片也相同
Set seed to -1, which will cause a new r: 设随机种子为 -1，代表每次都用新的随机数
Reuse seed from last generation, mostly: 复用上次生成时的随机种子，在那次是随机生成的情况下最有用
Seed of a different picture to be mixed: 另一张图片的随机种子，会被混入生成中
How strong of a variation to produce. At:
差异化剧烈程度
 为 0 时，没有效果
 为 1 时，会得到完全产自差异化随机种子的图片
（ancestral 采样方法除外，用它只会单纯地得到一些东西）
Make an attempt to produce a picture sim: 尝试产出一张图片，优先近似于在指定分辨率下以相同随机种子能生成的图片，并扩展或裁剪到当前分辨率
产生一张可以被密铺的图片
Use a two step process to partially crea: 分两步处理，先在较小分辨率下部分地创建一张图片，放大，再在不改变构图的情况下改进细节
Number of sampling steps for upscaled pi: Number of sampling steps for upscaled picture. If 0, uses same as for original.
Determines how little respect the algori:
决定算法对提供图片的重视程度
为 0 时，不会改变图片内容
为 1 时，会得到一张无关图片
小于 1.0 的值会导致实际处理所用步数少于指定的采样步数
Adjusts the size of the image by multipl: Adjusts the size of the image by multiplying the original width and height by the selected value. Ignored if either Resize width to or Resize height to are non-zero.
Resizes image to this width. If 0, width: Resizes image to this width. If 0, width is inferred from either of two nearby sliders.
Resizes image to this height. If 0, heig: Resizes image to this height. If 0, height is inferred from either of two nearby sliders.
This text is used to rotate the feature: 此文本用于旋转图集嵌入的特征空间
用逗号分隔 X 轴的值
Paste available values into the field: Paste available values into the field
用逗号分隔 Y 轴的值
Write image to a directory (default - lo: 保存图片（默认在 log/images），并将生成参数存入 csv 文件
Resize image to target resolution. Unles: 缩放图片至目标分辨率，除非宽高匹配，否则得到的图片比例有误
Resize the image so that entirety of tar: 缩放图片以填满目标分辨率，裁剪多余的部分
Resize the image so that entirety of ima: 缩放图片使其整体在目标分辨率内，用图片里有的颜色填充空白区域
How much to blur the mask before process: 处理前对遮罩模糊的像素数
What to put inside the masked area befor: 处理前要在遮罩区域填入什么内容
fill it with latent space noise: 填入隐空间噪声（latent space noise）
fill it with latent space zeroes: 填入隐空间零点（latent space zeroes）
How many times to repeat processing an i: 处理图片并作为下次迭代输入的重复次数
In loopback mode, on each loop the denoi:
产物迭代模式中，每次迭代去噪强度（Denoising strength）会乘以该值
小于 1 意味着变化程度递减，故生成的图片序列收敛到一张固定图片；大于 1 意味着变化程度递增，故生成的图片序列变得越来越混乱
For SD upscale, how much overlap in pixe: 对于 SD 放大，表示图块间应重叠的像素数，图块重叠使得在合并回一张图片后没有明显可见的接缝
Leave blank to save images to the defaul: 留空以将图片保存到默认路径
Result = A * (1 - M) + B * M: 结果 R = A * (1 - M) + B * M
Result = A + (B - C) * M: 结果 R = A + (B - C) * M
Regular expression; if weights's name ma: Regular expression; if weights's name matches it, the weights is not written to the resulting checkpoint. Use ^model_ema to discard EMA weights.
If the number of tokens is more than the:
If the number of tokens is more than the number of vectors, some may be skipped.
Leave the textbox empty to start with zeroed out vectors
1st and last digit must be 0 and values: 1st and last digit must be 0 and values should be between 0 and 1. ex:'0, 0.01, 0'
Use following tags to define how filenam: Use following tags to define how filenames for images are chosen: [steps], [cfg], [prompt_hash], [prompt], [prompt_no_styles], [prompt_spaces], [width], [height], [styles], [sampler], [seed], [model_hash], [model_name], [prompt_words], [date], [datetime], [datetime<Format>], [datetime<Format><Time Zone>], [job_timestamp]; leave empty for default.
If this option is enabled, watermark wil:
开启此设置，则生成的图片中不会有水印
警告：若不添加水印，你的行为可能缺少道德
Use following tags to define how subdire: Use following tags to define how subdirectories for images and grids are chosen: [steps], [cfg],[prompt_hash], [prompt], [prompt_no_styles], [prompt_spaces], [width], [height], [styles], [sampler], [seed], [model_hash], [model_name], [prompt_words], [date], [datetime], [datetime<Format>], [datetime<Format><Time Zone>], [job_timestamp]; leave empty for default.
Restore low quality faces using GFPGAN n: 用 GFPGAN 神经网络修复低质量面部
This regular expression will be used ext:
此正则表达式用于从文件名中提取词语，这些词语会用下面选项中的字符串拼接起来，并入用于训练的标签文本
留空则保持原文件名
This string will be used to join split w: 若启用上面的选项，此字符串用于将切出的单词拼接成一行
Only applies to inpainting models. Deter:
只适用于局部重绘模型
决定了局部重绘和图生图时对原图遮罩的程度
1.0 为完全遮罩，是默认行为
0.0 为完全不遮罩
较小的值有助于保留图片的整体构图，但难以引起较大的变化
Early stopping parameter for CLIP model;:
控制 CLIP 模型提前终止的参数
1 为如往常一般终止在最后一层，2 为终止在倒数第二层，以此类推
When adding extra network such as Hypern: When adding extra network such as Hypernetwork or Lora to prompt, use this multiplier for it.
List of setting names, separated by comm:
设置名的列表，以英文逗号分隔，将其中的设置放入页面顶部快速访问栏而非通常的设置选项卡
设置名参见 modules/shared.py
应用设置后需重启
Comma-separated list of tab names; tabs: Comma-separated list of tab names; tabs listed here will appear in the extra networks UI first and in order lsited.
Cheap neural network approximation. Very: Cheap neural network approximation. Very fast compared to VAE, but produces pictures with 4 times smaller horizontal/vertical resolution and lower quality.
Very cheap approximation. Very fast comp: Very cheap approximation. Very fast compared to VAE, but produces pictures with 8 times smaller horizontal/vertical resolution and extremely low quality.
Ignores step count - uses a number of st: 忽略步数 - 具体步数由 CFG 和分辨率决定
Denoising Diffusion Implicit Models - be: Denoising Diffusion Implicit Models - 擅长局部重绘（Inpaint）
If this values is non-zero, it will be a:
若此值非零，在用带有 Eta 的采样方法时，它会被加入随机种子并用于初始化噪声的随机数生成器
可以用它来产生更多的图片变化
也可以用它来贴近其他软件生成的图片，要是你知道自己在做什么的话
